Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Mizu-chan, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm really that soft with Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't you act the same as anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san's the one who's a little weird. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san... might have liked Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I could see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she resents him for turning her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't think Yamamoto-san's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... maybe. She doesn't seem that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a big fan of her myself, but I do think she's a pretty reasonable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think Yano always restrains himself around Yamamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he has some hidden reason he feels guilty about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed like you couldn't really respond to Yamamoto-san, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I really didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heading home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop by the plaza on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a long-sleeved T-shirt I really wanna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many T-shirts do you need before you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me for buying so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so protective of me like before. It's unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really thought you were doing your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm telling you, you don't need to say that sort of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I stuck my nose into your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mean to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I am... I'm just being me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you try being kinder?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever she's around I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:56.22,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an7\c&H000000&\fscx117.5\fscy155\pos(249,46)}Recommended by the Ministry\N of Education?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:56.22,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\c&H000000&\fscx192.5\fscy171.25\pos(279,190)}The Peak\N of Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:56.22,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\c&H000000&\fscx103.75\fscy141.25\pos(421,393)}Class 1-7\N Calligraphy\N by Me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kohsaka, and I'm in charge of producing this class's short play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Peak of Hope".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This story is a masterpiece that will make anyone and everyone cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the culture festival right before our eyes, the rehearsals should be coming to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the real thing's happening the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't you think we've had enough rehearsals?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's hurry and get the real thing over with!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are some of the things I should be hearing in these final preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:11.84,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz340.824\pos(291,103)\fscx137.5\fscy123.75\b1\c&H3A4F68&}BUT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually nothing like that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's because...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-kun, you skipped too many rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's do this, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Yano really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like he has a drop of motivation in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't someone say he always gets things done when they need to get done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to put our faith in that, huh, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything... I won't say anything unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Starting from the scene on page 25!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing your sword on someone holding a mere hoe... I can see how the mighty warriors have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say anything untoward, but drop your weapon, and do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I cannot guarantee your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that reading?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put more feeling into it! Feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I don't really want to ask, but don't you have your lines memorized?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are so many long scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real thing's the day after tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get someone to hold up cue cards during the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memorize your lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't take care of things when they need to get done at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will we really be all right in time for the actual show?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, say something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the class president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that and this don't really have much to do with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm busy enough with my own role...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, please! It's the day after tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the day after tomorrow, cram as many lines as you can into your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to have it perfect. Perfect, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... my stomach's starting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how do you read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mount Kyokurin? Mount Kokurin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still only at that low level?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so protective of me like before. It's unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get some steamed meat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...understand Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...be able to talk like we did before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I heard a strange tale from a monk travelling the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He spoke of a golden lichen growing upon the peak of Mount Kyokurin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so holy that if one were to sow it elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would transform a wasteland into a land of abundant harvest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and all quarrels between people would vanish, and peace would flourish everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of this, people have called that peak upon Mount Kyokurin the "Peak of Hope".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano can really be amazing at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, that was wonderful! Your acting was spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing... I want to tell Yano that he's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be memorizing my lines right now! I have to get all three down! All three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're still as easy as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.82,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H6881BD&\frz15.868\frx18\fry332\fscx271.25\fscy317.5\pos(363,111)}School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's fame really is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this goes off well, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.13,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Book: The Peak of Hope
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still reading the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Yano, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he's changing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always doing things last minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure whether to call it airheadedness or what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:46.99,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Samurai, please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:54.18,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5F66A9&\frz341.93\fscx237.5\fscy175\frx352\fry22\pos(446,364)}N\Ne\Nr\Nv\No\Nu\Ns
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:54.18,test2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5F66A9&\fscx271.25\fscy182.5\frx0\fry338\pos(83,323)}N\Ne\Nr\Nv\No\Nu\Ns
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm just Village Girl #2 and I only have three lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wish he'd share some of his courage... sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there so many people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? They're all here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Yano-kun, we're counting on you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was my first line again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... I might've forgotten all my lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-First, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take deep breaths! Deep breaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just picture yourself doing it correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some water!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The script, the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have to read it! Yano will do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're almost up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're on standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-kun, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something unnecessary again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Br...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... there's something on that mountain over there. Er, what was it called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you mean Mount Kyokurin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah! That one, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to have this so-called... Umm... what was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The something-or-other peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Peak of Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though all of his lines are random...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience hasn't realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has such a way with words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that complete lack of stage fright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong in these serious events.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a pain, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! We beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so protective of me like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the mistake you're making it out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know which is the real Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.49,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H44586C&\b1\fscx205\fscy281.25\pos(93,453)}You're
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:15.49,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H44586C&\b1\fscx205\fscy281.25\pos(151,453)}up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Samurai, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I will! If I were as out of hand as you, I'd fall over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or could it be that they're all the real him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a huge success, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.29,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Swordfish
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, this is really heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it ends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.10,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The top of my ring came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the one you bought for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, just give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be impossible to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I liked it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you do--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He surprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, you jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person shouldn't go around telling people to "die" all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to actually die tomorrow in a car accident or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd feel bad, even though it wouldn't have been your fault, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if something convenient like that would--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell her that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different from the savage Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.07,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, saying "die" is so boringly simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boringly simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then how about, "I'll kill you, bitch"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi's of low character!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, we were speaking normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think dying's such an easy way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'd break a person's fingers one by one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then pull each of his nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just agree that you're a sadist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that when you die, you don't feel anything or know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that too boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It always feels like I'm about to understand him, but then he gets away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love confession time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that during things like this, couples step forward and dance cheek-to-cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if someone's confessing to Yano right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm especially good at...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you imagine if someone confessed to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, whoops. Wrong thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the ring's weird, I still feel kinda bad for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've put on weight, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't go on my thumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, on this finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're exchanging wedding rings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words they say at weddings sure are nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you take this woman to be your wife, and vow to love her forever?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we getting married out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It just slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But words aren't good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in that situation, I'd probably say something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please break my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy. Crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only say this once, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Far in the distance, I heard the sound of fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:23:03.98,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Jama da te wo futta ushirosugata anna ni mou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:16.50,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuugure no hitonami ni yurenagara chiisaku naru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:26.17,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga kureta kotoba wo hitotsuzutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:37.64,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Omoidashi me wo tojita Shiawasena omoi dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:48.49,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,koko ni aru hazu nano ni Fuan ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:58.12,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,doushite nano kokoro ga furueteru no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:10.59,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutaetai motto sou afureteru kono kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:22.15,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Suki dakara suki dakara zettai suki dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:39.16,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Furimuite kakedashite oikakete ikitai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:51.34,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuugure no sabishisa ga sonna yuuki nomikonda
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:25:00.73,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata no egao no naka ni watashi ha iru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.73,0:25:07.36,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sukoshi hanareta dakede
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:12.20,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoigo ni natta youna
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.20,0:25:19.41,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,kodomo mitai nakidashisou
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:26.29,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao nara konna omoi
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:32.97,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,shinakutemo sumu no ni na
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.97,0:25:34.51,Romaji ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Karappo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:23:03.98,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in the way. I waved my hand, but your back is
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:16.50,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,already swerving through the crowd of people and sinking into the evening sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:26.17,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I closed my eyes and began to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:37.64,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the words you told me. Only happy memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:48.49,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to be there, but I become anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:58.12,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my heart waver so?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:10.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you about my overflowing feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:22.15,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you, I love you, I love you more than anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:39.16,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to turn around, run after you, catch up with you, but
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:51.34,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,the sadness of the twilit sky swallowed my courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:25:00.73,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.73,0:25:07.36,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a short time after we've parted
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:12.20,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cry out like a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.20,0:25:19.41,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,lost child.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:26.29,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could be honest with myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.29,0:25:32.97,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't have had to go through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.97,0:25:34.51,english ED SS,,0000,0000,0000,,Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.85,0:25:34.92,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\c&HFDE2FF&\pos(450,377)\fscx86.25\fscy122.5}Episode 5 Preview . . .
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.40,0:25:07.36,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:09.57,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,As if it were a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.57,0:25:12.86,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...I saw the whole world\N change before my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.53,0:25:15.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano cast a spell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.49,0:25:17.95,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.95,0:25:20.70,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything\N you want for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.70,0:25:21.54,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.08,0:25:26.25,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a serious answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.88,0:25:30.67,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided on what\N I want for a Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.01,0:25:33.47,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a promise.
